Spendio - Money Sharing Tracker App - Legal Information: Lendio App is here to help to track and manage lending & borrowing money between friends & groups. However Spendio App will not ask you to pay using any ways except using payments through Apple App Store. Also, Spendio App does not require to submit any users personal data. All data inputted by user is stored only locally on users device. Spendio App cannot be held responsible for any successfull or unsuccessfull notifiying about users inputted data, such as information about lend / borrowed money. 
